    {# ── INTRO ── #}
    <section class="cs-pg-intro">
      <div class="cs-pg-intro__text">
        <h2 class="cs-section-label">Advance Your Research Career</h2>
        <p>
          Our postgraduate programmes provide advanced education and research opportunities in computer science.
          Whether you're interested in specialised coursework, original research, or making a lasting
          contribution to the field, we have a programme tailored to your goals — guided by world-class
          faculty with active research profiles.
        </p>
        <p>
          From Honours through to PhD, you'll work alongside leading researchers, access state-of-the-art
          facilities, and join a vibrant community of scholars in the heart of the Cape Winelands.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="cs-pg-intro__highlights">
        <div class="cs-pg-highlight">
          <span class="cs-pg-highlight__number">3</span>
          <span class="cs-pg-highlight__label">Degree Levels</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-pg-highlight">
          <span class="cs-pg-highlight__number">6+</span>
          <span class="cs-pg-highlight__label">Research Groups</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cs-pg-highlight">
          <span class="cs-pg-highlight__number">11</span>
          <span class="cs-pg-highlight__label">PG Modules</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    {# ── DEGREE PROGRAMMES ── #}
    <section class="cs-pg-degrees">
      <h2 class="cs-section-label cs-section-label--center">Our Programmes</h2>
      <p class="cs-pg-degrees__lead">Choose the level that matches your ambition and experience.</p>

      <div class="cs-pg-degrees__grid">
        <div class="cs-pg-degree-card">
          <div class="cs-pg-degree-card__top">
            <span class="cs-pg-degree-card__duration">1 Year Full-Time</span>
            <svg class="cs-pg-degree-card__icon" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--cs-gold)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M22 10v6M2 10l10-5 10 5-10 5z"/><path d="M6 12v5c3 3 9 3 12 0v-5"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-pg-degree-card__title">Honours</h3>
          <p class="cs-pg-degree-card__desc">
            An intensive programme combining 6 advanced modules (96 credits) with a compulsory
            programming project (32 credits). Ideal for bridging undergraduate and research-level study.
          </p>
          <ul class="cs-pg-degree-card__highlights">
            <li>6 advanced modules + project</li>
            <li>Prepares you for MSc or industry</li>
            <li>Part-time option available (2 years)</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/postgraduate/honours" class="cs-pg-degree-card__link">Explore Honours →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-pg-degree-card cs-pg-degree-card--featured">
          <span class="cs-pg-degree-card__badge">Research Focus</span>
          <div class="cs-pg-degree-card__top">
            <span class="cs-pg-degree-card__duration">2–3 Years</span>
            <svg class="cs-pg-degree-card__icon" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--cs-gold)" stroke-width="1.5"><path d="M2 3h6a4 4 0 0 1 4 4v14a3 3 0 0 0-3-3H2z"/><path d="M22 3h-6a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v14a3 3 0 0 1 3-3h7z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-pg-degree-card__title">Master's</h3>
          <p class="cs-pg-degree-card__desc">
            A research-intensive degree where you work with faculty mentors on an approved research
            topic, culminating in a thesis that contributes new knowledge to the field.
          </p>
          <ul class="cs-pg-degree-card__highlights">
            <li>Original research thesis (100+ pages)</li>
            <li>Expert faculty supervision</li>
            <li>Full-time or part-time (up to 5 years)</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/postgraduate/masters" class="cs-pg-degree-card__link">Explore Master's →</a>
        </div>

        <div class="cs-pg-degree-card">
          <div class="cs-pg-degree-card__top">
            <span class="cs-pg-degree-card__duration">3–4 Years</span>
            <svg class="cs-pg-degree-card__icon" width="36" height="36" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--cs-gold)" stroke-width="1.5"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="cs-pg-degree-card__title">PhD</h3>
          <p class="cs-pg-degree-card__desc">
            The highest research degree — designed for exceptional scholars committed to making original
            contributions to computer science through independently conducted research.
          </p>
          <ul class="cs-pg-degree-card__highlights">
            <li>Doctoral dissertation (200+ pages)</li>
            <li>Publication in top-tier venues</li>
            <li>International collaboration</li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/postgraduate/phd" class="cs-pg-degree-card__link">Explore PhD →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

